
               ==================================
                   HELP FOR VHDL COMMAND KEYS
               ==================================

VHDL Major Mode Bindings:
----------------------------

key              binding
---              -------

RET		 vhdl-newline
,		 vhdl-stutter-comma
.		 vhdl-stutter-period
]		 vhdl-stutter-close-bracket
[		 vhdl-stutter-open-bracket
'		 vhdl-stutter-quote
;		 vhdl-stutter-semicolon
-		 vhdl-stutter-dash
SPC		 vhdl-outer-space
TAB		 vhdl-tab-or-dabbrev
C-c		 Prefix Command
DEL		 backward-delete-char-untabify

C-c a            vhdl-architecture                    
C-c C-a          vhdl-array                           
C-c A            vhdl-assert                          
C-c <            vhdl-backward-to-same-indent         
C-c d            vhdl-block                           
C-c c            vhdl-case                            
C-c C            vhdl-component                       
C-c C-c          vhdl-display-comment                 
C-c E            vhdl-else                            
C-c I            vhdl-elsif                           
C-c e            vhdl-entity                          
C-c x            vhdl-exit                            
C-c f            vhdl-for-loop                        
C-c >            vhdl-forward-to-same-indent          
C-c C-f          vhdl-function-spec                   
C-c h            vhdl-help                            
C-c i            vhdl-if                              
C-c -            vhdl-inline-comment                  
C-c l            vhdl-loop                            
C-c k            vhdl-package-body                    
C-c C-k          vhdl-package-spec                    
C-c (            vhdl-paired-parens                   
C-c C-p          vhdl-procedure-spec                  
C-c C-r          vhdl-record                          
 ]               vhdl-stutter-close-bracket           
 ,               vhdl-stutter-comma                   
 -               vhdl-stutter-dash                    
 [               vhdl-stutter-open-bracket            
 .               vhdl-stutter-period                  
  '              vhdl-stutter-quote                   
 ;               vhdl-stutter-semicolon               
C-c C-s          vhdl-subtype                         
C-c t            vhdl-tabsize                         
C-c C-t          vhdl-type                            
C-c TAB          vhdl-untab                           
C-c C-u          vhdl-use                             
C-c v            vhdl-variables                       
C-c C-w          vhdl-when                            
C-c w            vhdl-while-loop                      
C-c @            add-vhdl-function                    
C-c #            write-vhdl-function                  
